{
  "id": "RAW_acb7a3a1",
  "title": "OpenAI 正在制造系统性风险：老子不会死，要死一起死",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzNDQxOTU2MQ==&mid=2247506834&idx=1&sn=57560fe910579fa8161867fc43647854",
  "date": "2025-10-12 15:19:00",
  "author": "赛博禅心",
  "siteName": "赛博禅心",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF!important;font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Helvetica Neue', 'Arial', sans-serif;max-width: 500px;margin: 0 auto;padding: 0px;background-image: linear-gradient(#F5F5F5 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, #F5F5F5 1px, transparent 1px)!important;background-size: 20px 20px;overflow: hidden;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"padding: 20px;\">\n    <div style=\"text-align: left;border-bottom: 2px solid black;padding-bottom: 15px;margin-bottom: 25px;\">\n     <p style=\"font-size: 14px;color: #555555;margin: 5px 0 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">本周重点还是讨论OpenAI，但可能更适合投资的朋友一起讨论。</span></p>\n     <p style=\"font-size: 14px;color: #555555;margin: 5px 0 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">动态里介绍了下 figure03 和 jina。</span></p>\n     <p style=\"font-size: 14px;color: #555555;margin: 5px 0 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">内容里推荐给产品经理的 2 篇实用文章，同时锦秋集把明浩老师贴让我们一起学习的 report 给编译出来了，特别好。下次我有啥认真想看的，也先发给她们试试。思路打开。</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"text-align: left;margin-bottom: 25px;\">\n     <h2 style=\"margin:0 0 15px;font-weight:700;border-left:4px solid #F26522;padding-left:10px;font-size:20px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(61, 167, 66);\">OpenAI</span></span></h2>\n     <div style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;text-align: left;\">\n      <h3 style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;margin: 0 0 10px;\"><span leaf=\"\">1. Dev day</span></h3>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.7;\"><b><span leaf=\"\">a. 一句话说下发了啥：</span></b><span leaf=\"\">ChatGPT 终于搞平台战略了 app inside ChatGPT；都说是抄了 coze的agent kit；codeX 的正式版；和模型gpt-5，sora2&amp;sora2 pro， real-time mini 的 API。顺便晒了个数据，服，班长就是班长。</span></p>\n      <p><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"306680973\" alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 4px;box-sizing: border-box;margin: 15px 0;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a719e673&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FZxClMzoCxAsXicO9bibia8TcsfgJysluIZ45HlsjOmXhHen8EOpiakByI4voS18K6lEoVO2FDB8evcc5ksoGUO2iaibQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.7;\"><b><span leaf=\"\">b. 介绍的文章实在已经满坑满谷啦，我就懒得总结了。</span></b><span leaf=\"\">愿意看详情的点大聪明的文：<a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzNDQxOTU2MQ==&amp;mid=2247506639&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=81a8965c65b4ec642098b31a40e9e8d0&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"OpenAI 年度发布会：Agent平台/Sora API/第三方接入ChatGPT/... 讲的没讲的，都在这了\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">OpenAI 年度发布会：Agent平台/Sora API/第三方接入ChatGPT/... 讲的没讲的，都在这了</a></span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.7;\"><b><span leaf=\"\">c. 因为这张图，让我觉得 OpenAI 的路径确实有点像 Windows。<img data-w=\"3582\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3417085427135678\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=344da9ea&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZxClMzoCxAsXicO9bibia8TcsfgJysluIZ45n6XmSsZI7cWkFcc5VACLsiaIrN5CG9cBiczJiclFMoj51v2N5pdCsmvg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></b></p>\n     </div>\n     <div style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;text-align: left;\">\n      <h3 style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;margin: 0 0 10px;\"><span leaf=\"\">2. &nbsp;跟 AMD 的合作</span></h3>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">苏妈美滋滋发出了朋友圈。</span></p>\n      <p><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"306680969\" alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6268518518518519\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 4px;box-sizing: border-box;margin: 15px 0;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9bf6150e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZxClMzoCxAsXicO9bibia8TcsfgJysluIZ4vK7SC4PHenBIx5Mwxeptto12ssCtJuU30sY3ib51la8P6EGhMvicdV9w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">Which means 3000 亿左右的 capex 支出。括号，上次 NV 和 OpenAI 是10GW。这个交易的背后，OpenAI 能拿到 10% 的 AMD 股份。有点乱。</span></p>\n     </div>\n     <div style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;text-align: left;\">\n      <h3 style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;margin: 0 0 10px;\"><span leaf=\"\">3. 所以，这礼拜最出名的图可能是这张。</span></h3>\n      <p><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"306680971\" alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.2222222222222223\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 4px;box-sizing: border-box;margin: 15px 0;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=384be993&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FZxClMzoCxAsXicO9bibia8TcsfgJysluIZ4AyYkBNMh9ZDRbks99QZ0f4LuHYApkiaMFmvs5EKqOWibZ7YxIyvomwhA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">实话实说，我看到这图的第一反应是check自己的持仓，哈哈哈。解读嘛, 网上已经很多了，我试了试Claude，它第一反应的冠冕堂皇说法是：这个生态系统展现了AI产业\"你中有我，我中有你\"的深度整合格局，资本、算力和应用形成了高度互锁的价值网络。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">啧🙄，我对 Claude 这一说法表示了不服，我说，这泡沫多大啊你看啊喂。嗯它跟我吵了几轮之后，我俩最后达成一致的结论是：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(61, 167, 66);\">这是一个有实体支撑的泡沫 —— 既有真实技术价值，但估值已严重脱离短期盈利能力</span>。关键要看：</span><span leaf=\"\">- 企业AI应用何时产生实质ROI</span><span leaf=\"\">- 消费者是否愿意长期为AI订阅付费</span><span leaf=\"\">- 算力成本能否大幅下降</span><span leaf=\"\">让我们拭目以待。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin:30px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7558007329975828482;font-weight: bold;color: #034F46 !important;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-author&quot;:&quot;dui!&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: inherit;font-weight: 400;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;margin: 0 0px;margin-bottom: 35px;padding: 35px 25px;border: 2px solid rgba(3, 79, 70, 1);background-color: rgba(250, 250, 250, 1);border-radius: 12px;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;color: inherit;margin: 0;min-height: 20px;letter-spacing: auto;color: inherit;color: inherit;font-size: inheritpx;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;font-weight: 400;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: #1A1A1A;font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;margin: 30px 0;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: inherit;author: 7558007329975828482;font-weight: bold;color: #034F46 !important;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\">还有两篇美国人自己的评论值得一翻。</span></span></span></p>\n     </div>\n     <div style=\"border-radius:4px;border:1px solid #EEEEEE;padding:15px;margin-bottom:20px;text-align:left;\">\n      <h4 style=\"margin: 0 0 10px;font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">1. 一篇是：OpenAI's Money Trust: Engineering Systemic Risk as Strategy</span></h4>\n      <div style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:10px;margin-bottom:10px;\">\n       <p style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;font-size: 13px;line-height: 1.6;margin: 0 0 10px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">TL;DR</span>&nbsp;：OpenAI’s real strategy isn’t just platform dominance — it’s structural indispensability. Like J.P. Morgan in 1907, OpenAI is positioning itself as the central node of an entire ecosystem, creating mutual dependencies across chips, cloud, developers, and users.</span></p>\n       <p style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;font-size: 13px;line-height: 1.6;margin: 0 0 10px;\"><span leaf=\"\">The massive multi-billion dollar deals with AMD, Nvidia, and Oracle aren’t just scale plays — they’re engineered entanglements. These deals bind OpenAI’s survival to the financial, operational, and political interests of other major players, making failure systemically dangerous.</span></p>\n       <p style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;font-size: 13px;line-height: 1.6;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">This isn’t recklessness, it’s strategy: manufacture systemic risk so that rescue becomes inevitable. OpenAI is betting it can become too interconnected to fail before capital dries up or the tech shifts — forcing governments and markets to preserve its existence, just like they did with Morgan’s trust.</span></p>\n      </div>\n      <p style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.7;margin: 0 0 10px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">中译</span>：OpenAI 的真正战略不仅仅是平台主导地位——而是结构性不可或缺。就像 1907 年的 J.P.摩根一样，OpenAI 正将自己定位为整个生态系统的中心节点，在芯片、云、开发者和用户之间创造相互依赖关系。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.7;margin: 0 0 10px;\"><span leaf=\"\">与 AMD、Nvidia 和 Oracle 的数十亿美元交易不仅仅是规模游戏——它们是精心设计的纠缠。这些交易将 OpenAI 的生存与其他主要参与者的财务、运营和政治利益绑定在一起，使得失败在系统上变得危险。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.7;margin: 0 0 10px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这不是鲁莽，而是战略：制造系统性风险，使得救助变得不可避免。OpenAI 正在押注它可以在资本枯竭或技术转变之前变得过于互联而无法失败——迫使政府和市场维护其存在，就像他们对摩根的信托所做的那样。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">原文很精彩，回顾一段历史来对照当前的 AI 局势，推荐阅读 ：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\"><a href=\"https://substack.com/inbox/post/175519958\" target=\"_blank\">https://substack.com/inbox/post/175519958</a></span></span></p>\n     </div>\n     <div style=\"border-radius:4px;border:1px solid #EEEEEE;padding:15px;margin-bottom:20px;text-align:left;\">\n      <h4 style=\"margin: 0 0 10px;font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">2. 另一篇是Ben Thompson 的，就叫 OpenAI’s Windows play。</span></h4>\n      <p style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.7;margin: 0 0 10px;\"><span leaf=\"\">话不多说，我搬个图大家就知道 Ben 的核心观点了，是的，OpenAI 在下一盘大棋，目标就是 AI 时代的操作系统，让所有的应用和服务都构建在它的基础之上。</span></p>\n      <p><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"306680972\" alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5537037037037037\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 4px;box-sizing: border-box;margin: 15px 0;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=338ea427&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZxClMzoCxAsXicO9bibia8TcsfgJysluIZ4ibcasdrYrnibbiaUSsAD8oqXDaFUR1Mawoy5ktxeNF3EwcjW2Ic21ibFEg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n      <p style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.7;margin: 0 0 10px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这张图一放，显得 OpenAI 找 AMD 合作就很合理，同时也不得不说，AMD 挺能活。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\"><a href=\"https://stratechery.com/2025/openais-windows-play/\" target=\"_blank\">https://stratechery.com/2025/openais-windows-play/</a></span></span></p>\n     </div>\n     <div style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;text-align: left;\">\n      <h3 style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;margin: 0 0 10px;\"><span leaf=\"\">最后，让我们看看<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">男</span>正主自己是怎么来画饼的！</span></h3>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.7;\"><b><span leaf=\"\">1. YouTube 里跟 a16z 唠了 50 分钟</span></b><span leaf=\"\">，什么 AGI，能源，技术未来，空一点。我纯喜欢或者说是期待他在8 分钟开始说的那些观点：</span></p>\n      <ul style=\"margin: 0 0 10px;padding-left: 20px;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.7;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n       <li style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">LUI 的潜力还远远没有被挖掘完（产品经理颤抖吧！）</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;font-size: 13px;color: #555;\"><span leaf=\"\">What a chat interface can do for you it's like nowhere near saturated。</span></span></p>\n       </li>\n       <li style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">未来的AI-人类界面可能包括实时渲染的视频和能理解用户情境的智能硬件设备 。</span></p>\n       </li>\n       <li style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">他最期待的AI能力是成为“AI科学家” ，未来两年内AI将能在科学研究中做出重要发现</span></p>\n       </li>\n      </ul>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 视频链接 ：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JfE1Wun9xkk\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JfE1Wun9xkk</a></span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.7;\"><b><span leaf=\"\">2. 还有一篇stratechery跟他的访谈</span></b><span leaf=\"\">，核心思想是一致的：构建AGI、大规模投入基础设施。但在讲得更实在，更聚焦和清晰。</span></p>\n      <div style=\"padding:12px;margin:10px 0;border-left:3px solid #ced4da;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;text-align:left;\">\n       <p style=\"margin:0;\"><span leaf=\"\">对于Ben 的 Windows 比喻，Sam 回复说 &nbsp;I always struggle with the historical analogies because I always get caught up on where there’s differences that I really care about or whatever.（学到了啊！真是高情商啊！）</span></p>\n      </div>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">原文链接：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\"><a href=\"https://stratechery.com/2025/an-interview-with-openai-ceo-sam-altman-about-devday-and-the-ai-buildout/\" target=\"_blank\">https://stratechery.com/2025/an-interview-with-openai-ceo-sam-altman-about-devday-and-the-ai-buildout/</a></span></span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"text-align: left;margin-bottom: 25px;\">\n     <h2 style=\"margin:0 0 15px;font-weight:700;border-left:4px solid #F26522;padding-left:10px;font-size:20px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(61, 167, 66);\">动态</span></span></h2>\n     <div style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;text-align: left;\">\n      <h3 style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;margin: 0 0 10px;\"><span leaf=\"\">1. Figure 03 发了。确实帅，看完有种梦想照进现实的意思。它：</span></h3>\n      <ul style=\"margin: 0 0 10px;padding-left: 20px;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.7;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n       <li style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">能洗衣服了（洗衣机用得比我家属还明白，洗完还能叠好！</span></p>\n       </li>\n       <li style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">能刷碗了（不怕水且没 cei还知道要晾水</span></p>\n       </li>\n       <li style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">能端茶倒水啦（捏杯子恰到好处</span></p>\n       </li>\n       <li style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">能自己跑去给自己充电了（除了走来走去肢体动作还是有点僵，看得我特别捉急</span></p>\n       </li>\n       <li style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">还能换衣服哈哈哈哈哈（我想给它来个粉紫小裙子行吗</span></p>\n       </li>\n      </ul>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">大家还是看视频吧，原理啥的不展开。看完这么酷的机器人，我现在只有消费者脑袋，买它。</span></p>\n      <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n     </div>\n     <div style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;text-align: left;\">\n      <h3 style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;margin: 0 0 10px;\"><span leaf=\"\">2. Elastic 收了 Jina</span></h3>\n      <ul style=\"margin: 0 0 10px;padding-left: 20px;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.7;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n       <li style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">开源的Elastic search 大名鼎鼎，所在公司是个正经八百的上市企业，做企业搜索，数据分析，可观测，安全等解决方案。</span></p>\n       </li>\n       <li style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">Jina.AI成立于 20 年，搞了些开源的多模态&amp;多语言 embeding，reranker 的小模型。这两年还 蛮火的其实。</span></p>\n       </li>\n       <li style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">这个收购在我看来，就属于很互补的那种强强联合。Elastic 在向量检索，RAG 跑得慢，并完后Jina 的肖博士就是 Elastic 的 AI VP，他后面再开发的模型就能跟 Elastic search 的向量数据库做深度集成，也能通过 Elastic cloud 直接卖 inference 服务。挺好的。</span></p>\n       </li>\n      </ul>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;官宣 blog 在这里：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\"><a href=\"https://www.elastic.co/blog/elastic-jina-ai\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.elastic.co/blog/elastic-jina-ai</a></span></span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"text-align: left;margin-bottom: 25px;\">\n     <h2 style=\"margin:0 0 15px;font-weight:700;border-left:4px solid #F26522;padding-left:10px;font-size:20px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(61, 167, 66);\">内容</span></span></h2>\n     <div style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;text-align: left;\">\n      <h3 style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;margin: 0 0 10px;\"><span leaf=\"\">1. 先上报告吧。air street capital 300 页的《State of AI Report 2025》 （人工智能状况报告）</span></h3>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">a. 不想 tldr ，里头观点太多。自己看。<a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg4Nzc3NjY0Mw==&amp;mid=2247498749&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=0afde70774b2167573d807962d3645ae&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"Air Street Capital 300页AI报告：拆解 AI 从“前沿研究”跃迁为全球化“工业力量”的200 条线索\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">Air Street Capital 300页AI报告：拆解 AI 从“前沿研究”跃迁为全球化“工业力量”的200 条线索</a></span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">b. 除开报告本身的 insight，锦秋的这三个命题掐挺准。希望锦秋集后面少发点自己的小广告，多整点深度内容。比心。</span></p>\n      <p><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"306680970\" alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.32\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"650\" style=\"display: block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 4px;box-sizing: border-box;margin: 15px 0;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=beb1f677&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZxClMzoCxAsXicO9bibia8TcsfgJysluIZ4lD1xqiawoHdFtungqoY2ibMxnxYdUKykrwAicpAHhRrqeKzq8FJuTFS6A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n     </div>\n     <div style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;text-align: left;\">\n      <h3 style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;margin: 0 0 10px;\"><span leaf=\"\">2. OpenAI academy 的一篇亲手喂饭贴：ChatGPT for product。</span></h3>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">a. 没什么好总结的，就是捡着抄的意思：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\"><a href=\"https://academy.openai.com/public/clubs/work-users-ynjqu/resources/use-cases-product\" target=\"_blank\">https://academy.openai.com/public/clubs/work-users-ynjqu/resources/use-cases-product</a></span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">b. 看到这段，感觉我的若干盆友会很开心。</span></p>\n      <p><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"306680976\" alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.22962962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 4px;box-sizing: border-box;margin: 15px 0;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=45fad260&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZxClMzoCxAsXicO9bibia8TcsfgJysluIZ46Jd6Ybb7t1uQj58LnoLdWOXiaQ96pRUFAMUNCdxxrbElczxkK2evfrA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n     </div>\n     <div style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;text-align: left;\">\n      <h3 style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;margin: 0 0 10px;\"><span leaf=\"\">3. 肯尼的长文：做 AI 测评 2 年多总结出来的 25 条核心认知。</span></h3>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">a. 原文链接&nbsp;<a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzk2NDc3MDQyNQ==&amp;mid=2247483874&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=57b462f4072c58a065d86c574662d859&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"长文更新 | 做AI产品2年多总结出来的25条核心认知\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">长文更新 | 做AI产品2年多总结出来的25条核心认知</a></span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">b. 他更新的这个部分，正巧我们也正在经历，深有同感：</span></p>\n      <div style=\"padding:12px;margin:10px 0;border-left:3px solid #ced4da;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;text-align:left;\">\n       <p style=\"margin:0;\"><span leaf=\"\">- 找到Model-Product-Market-Fit最关键，模型能力（现状&amp;未来）匹配用户需求（存量&amp;增量）</span><span leaf=\"\">- 用户需求是渐变的光谱，按过去的旧分类，AI只能替代存量解决方案，无法创造增量市场</span><span leaf=\"\">- 给用户交付一个结果，而非单纯做体验，通过管理用户预期，收敛场景，最终满足和超出用户预期</span><span leaf=\"\">- 产品框架要最大化拿到模型进步的红利，产品不在于弥补模型的不足，而在于充分发挥模型在目标场景的作用</span><span leaf=\"\">- 把模型当做人，一个非常聪明但一张白纸的人，在教模型干活之前，先想想人是怎么做事的，然后帮助它landing</span><span leaf=\"\">- 接受失控，相信模型，相信用户，相信社区，然后会见证很多超出计划和预期的美妙结果</span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"text-align: left;margin-bottom: 25px;border-top: 1px solid #EEEEEE;padding-top: 25px;\">\n     <h2 style=\"margin:0 0 15px;font-weight:700;border-left:4px solid #F26522;padding-left:10px;font-size:20px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(61, 167, 66);\">段子</span></span></h2>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"306680977\" data-ratio=\"0.6152241918665277\" style=\"display: block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 4px;box-sizing: border-box;margin: 15px 0;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"959\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1f950f08&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZxClMzoCxAsXicO9bibia8TcsfgJysluIZ4pE9Y6kHYDc9ic90wO9RhkpHBwiaakJzGdRvxGPibwvTBjp6ic6uOAJnPqA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章深度剖析 OpenAI 的平台战略与行业绑定的“系统性风险”策略，并结合 Dev Day 发布、AMD 合作及 Sam Altman 访谈，探讨其成为 AI 时代“操作系统”的野心。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章深度剖析 OpenAI 的平台战略与行业绑定的“系统性风险”策略，并结合 Dev Day 发布、AMD 合作及 Sam Altman 访谈，探讨其成为 AI 时代“操作系统”的野心。",
  "summary": "文章围绕 OpenAI 的近期动态展开，重点分析了 Dev Day 发布会的内容，概述了 ChatGPT 平台化、Sora API 等动态，并将其与 Windows 的平台战略进行类比。核心观点是 OpenAI 正通过与 AMD、Nvidia 等巨头的数十亿美元交易，制造“结构性不可或缺”的系统性风险，旨在绑定整个 AI 生态系统，使其“大而不倒”，如同 1907 年的 J.P.摩根。文章引用 Ben Thompson 的观点，进一步强调 OpenAI 欲成为 AI 时代操作系统的野心。此外，文章还分享了 Sam Altman 对 AGI、LUI 潜力和 AI 科学家角色的展望，以及对近期 Figure 03 机器人进展、Elastic 收购 Jina.AI 等行业动态的评论，并推荐了 Air Street Capital 的 AI 报告和 AI 产品测评经验，为读者提供了多维度的行业洞察。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "OpenAI 正通过战略性交易制造“系统性风险”以确保其行业地位",
      "explanation": "通过与芯片和云巨头的深度绑定，OpenAI 使其生存与整个生态系统的主要参与者利益挂钩，形成“大而不倒”的局面，迫使市场和政府在危机时进行救助。"
    },
    {
      "point": "OpenAI 的长期目标是成为 AI 时代的“操作系统”",
      "explanation": "效仿微软 Windows 的成功路径，OpenAI 旨在构建一个基础平台，让所有 AI 应用和服务都围绕其构建，从而掌握生态系统的核心控制权。"
    },
    {
      "point": "未来的 AI-人类交互（LUI）和 AI 科学家将是重要发展方向",
      "explanation": "Sam Altman 展望 AI 的潜力远超当前，特别是在用户界面（LUI）的创新和 AI 在科学研究中做出重大发现的能力，这将深刻改变人机互动和科研模式。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "OpenAI 的真正战略不仅仅是平台主导地位------而是结构性不可或缺。",
    "这不是鲁莽，而是战略：制造系统性风险，使得救助变得不可避免。",
    "OpenAI 正在押注它可以在资本枯竭或技术转变之前变得过于互联而无法失败------迫使政府和市场维护其存在，就像他们对摩根的信托所做的那样。",
    "OpenAI 在下一盘大棋，目标就是 AI 时代的操作系统，让所有的应用和服务都构建在它的基础之上。",
    "未来的 AI-人类界面可能包括实时渲染的视频和能理解用户情境的智能硬件设备。"
  ],
